title: condensed sans serif with interesting angled edges
content:
This is probably an obvious one, but it hasn't crossed my path before. Anyone know what the font is or name any that are similar?  
Thank you in advance.

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150410094438im_/http:/typophile.com/files/font_5248.jpg)
author: Rawshock Design

comments.content: Don't have enough time to dig this case but as there are many fonts in the same ballpark, trying to have a look to [this list](http://web.archive.org/web/20150410094438/http:/typophile.com/node/105488#comment-562631) might be useful.
